        Creates a new instance of Survey
        Parameters:
        code - Survey Code to be used
        description - Survey Description to be used
        targetAudience - Survey Target Type to be used
        codes - Survey List of codes for the Target Audience. Contains a list of brands or categories or products etc.
        targetFirstDate - Defines the Time Interval for the Target Audience
        targetSecondDate - Defines the Time Interval for the Target Audience
        firstDate - First Date of the Time Interval
        secondDate - Second Date of the Time Interval
